        <section class="content">
            <div id="introduction" class="section">
                <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>Welcome to <strong>Student Hub</strong>. Your privacy is critically important to us. This policy explains how we handle your academic and personal information.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="data-collection" class="section">
                <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
                <p>To provide a personalized experience, we collect the following:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Account Info:</strong> Name, university email, and student ID.</li>
                    <li><strong>Academic Data:</strong> Course enrollments and schedule preferences.</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with our study tools.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="usage" class="section">
                <h2>3. How We Use Data</h2>
                <p>We use your data to synchronize your calendar, provide course recommendations, and facilitate peer-to-peer collaboration.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="security" class="section">
                <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement industry-standard encryption (AES-256) to ensure your data is protected against unauthorized access.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="rights" class="section">
                <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the right to export your data or delete your account at any time through the "Settings" panel.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
